00:00:33.570 --> 00:00:38.590
And while I was there, I saw this incredible,
stylish piece that just caught my eye.

00:00:38.590 --> 00:00:40.712
Look at this: It's beautiful.

00:00:40.712 --> 00:00:44.520
It's kinda got this tie-dye, this horizontal
kind of tie-dye Balinese effect.

00:00:44.520 --> 00:00:47.579
The price tag, unfortunately, was a little
bit steep.

00:00:47.579 --> 00:00:55.039
So I decided to go for it and make my own
version on my front lawn with absolutely no

00:00:55.039 --> 00:00:56.820
prior experience.

